      "title": "Anurath for the presidential battle",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Anura Kumara Dissanayake, the leader of Thajanata Vimukti Peramuna, has also joined as a candidate for the election of a new President in the Parliament.",
        "Representing the National People's Force, he joins the presidential battle. The election of the members of parliament to elect a new president is scheduled to be held on the 20th."
      ],
